---
import LegalLayout from "../layouts/LegalLayout.astro";

export const prerender = true;
---

<LegalLayout
	title="Privacy Policy"
	description="How PEOPB handles information on peopb.com."
	path="/privacy"
	lastUpdated="July 10, 2026"
>
	<h2>What this policy covers</h2>
	<p>
		This policy covers peopb.com only, the PEOPB company website. It does not
		cover our products. Aseda Church Suite and its applications (Guanhwɛfo,
		Logos, Presence, Steward, Store) collect and process member, attendance,
		and financial data under their own privacy policy, published on their own
		site.
	</p>

	<h2>What we collect</h2>
	<p>
		The contact form on this site opens your own email client with a
		pre-filled message addressed to peopbghana@gmail.com. We do not receive
		or store anything you type into that form on our own servers, it only
		reaches us if you send the resulting email.
	</p>
	<p>
		We do not use cookies, analytics, or tracking scripts on peopb.com.
	</p>

	<h2>Third-party links</h2>
	<p>
		This site links to WhatsApp and to asedachurchsuite.com. Once you leave
		peopb.com, that service's own privacy policy applies, not this one.
	</p>

	<h2>Contact</h2>
	<p>
		Questions about this policy: <a href="mailto:peopbghana@gmail.com">peopbghana@gmail.com</a>.
	</p>
</LegalLayout>
